    dc:description "FIGURES 1‒5. Adults of Macrobathra spp. 1. M. micacea sp. nov., holotype; 2. M. aequidistans sp. nov., holotype; 3. M. afflata sp. nov., holotype; 4. M. arneutis; 5. M. myrocoma. All males. Scales = 2.0 mm." ;
